result.title: App crashes when opening the settings menu
result.steps: 1.Open the app. 2.Tap on the settings icon. 3.App crashes immediately.
result.expected: Settings menu should open without crashing.
result.actual: App crashes immediately when settings menu is opened.

result.title: Text input field does not accept characters
result.steps: Go to the login page. Try to type in the username field. Characters do not appear.
result.expected: The text input field should accept characters.
result.actual: No characters appear when typing in the input field.

result.title: Navigation bar disappears after scrolling
result.steps:
1. Open the app.
2. Scroll down on the homepage.
3. The navigation bar disappears.
result.expected: The navigation bar should remain visible while scrolling.
result.actual: The navigation bar disappears after scrolling.

result.title: Images fail to load in gallery view
result.steps: 1. Go to the gallery page. 2. Try to load images. 3. Images fail to load or display as broken links.
result.expected: Images should load correctly in gallery view.
result.actual: Images do not load and show as broken links.

result.title: Error message appears on checkout page.
result.steps: 1. Add items to cart. 2. Proceed to checkout. 3. An error message appears during payment.

result.title: Dropdown menu not responsive on mobile devices
result.steps:
1. Open the website on mobile.
2. Try to click on the dropdown menu.
3. The dropdown menu does not respond.
result.expected: Dropdown menu should be clickable and functional on mobile devices.
result.actual: Dropdown menu is unresponsive on mobile devices.

result.title: User profile picture upload fails
result.steps:
1. Go to the user profile page.
2. Click 'Upload Picture'.
3. Upload a profile picture.
4. The image fails to upload.
result.expected: The profile picture should upload successfully without any error messages.
result.actual: The image fails to upload, and no error message appears.

result.title: Slow loading time on search results page
result.steps: 1. Go to the search page. 2. Enter a search term. 3. The search results page takes several seconds to load.

result.title: Text formatting issue in the blog editor
result.steps:
1. Open the blog editor.
2. Try to change the text color.
3. Text does not change color properly.

result.title: Page layout breaks on smaller screens
result.steps: 1. Open the website on a mobile device. 2. Navigate to the homepage. 3. The page layout breaks and becomes unreadable.
result.expected: Page layout should be responsive and readable on all screen sizes.
result.actual: Page layout breaks on smaller screens, making content difficult to read.

result.title: Submit button does not work on the contact form
result.steps:
1. Open the contact form.
2. Fill in all fields.
3. Click the submit button.
4. Nothing happens.
result.expected: The form should submit successfully and confirm submission to the user.
result.actual: Nothing happens when clicking the submit button.

result.title: Audio not playing on video page
result.steps: 1. Open the video page. 2. Play any video. 3. The video plays, but there is no audio.
result.expected: The video should play with audio.
result.actual: The video plays, but there is no audio.

result.title: Image carousel not working on homepage
result.steps: 1. Go to the homepage. 2. Try to navigate the image carousel. 3. Carousel does not move or change images.
result.expected: The image carousel should be functional and allow users to navigate between images.
result.actual: The image carousel does not respond to user input.

result.title: Password reset link not working
result.steps: 1. Go to the password reset page. 2. Enter email and submit request. 3. No email is received.

result.title: Pop-up notification not disappearing after action
result.steps: 1. Trigger a pop-up notification. 2. Perform the action to dismiss it. 3. The notification stays on the screen.

result.title: Error loading user profile page.
result.steps: 1. Login to the account. 2. Go to the profile page. 3. The page fails to load, showing an error message.

result.title: Search bar not functioning after update
result.steps:
1. Open the search page.
2. Try entering a search query.
3. Search bar does not register input.

result.title: Page layout is distorted on mobile devices
result.steps: 1. Open the website on a mobile device. 2. The page layout is misaligned, causing content to be unreadable.
result.expected: The page layout should be responsive and readable on mobile devices, with all content properly aligned and visible.
result.actual: The page layout is distorted on mobile devices, causing content to overlap or become hidden, making it unreadable.

result.title: Video player controls missing on fullscreen mode
result.steps:
(1) Open the video page.
(2) Click on the fullscreen button.
(3) Video controls are no longer visible in fullscreen mode.
result.expected: Video controls should remain visible when in fullscreen mode.
result.actual: Video controls are no longer visible in fullscreen mode.

result.title: Form validation error not showing
result.steps:
1. Open the contact form.
2. Leave a required field blank and submit.
3. No validation error appears.
result.expected: The form should display a validation error when a required field is left blank.
result.actual: No validation error appears, and the form is submitted incorrectly.

result.title: Pop-up modal freezes after clicking close button
result.steps:
1. Open the website.
2. Click on any pop-up modal.
3. Click the close button.
4. The modal freezes and does not close.

result.title: User login fails after password change
result.steps: 1. Change your password. 2. Try to log in with the new password. 3. Login fails.
result.expected: The user should be able to log in with the new password after changing it.
result.actual: Login fails even after changing the password successfully.

result.title: Broken link in footer section
result.steps: 1. Scroll down to the footer section. 2. Click on any of the links in the footer. 3. The link redirects to a 404 error page.
result.expected: Footer links should lead to valid pages without redirecting to 404 error pages.

result.title: Text alignment issue in product description
result.steps:
1. Go to the product page.
2. Look at the product description.
3. Text is misaligned.
result.expected: The text should be aligned properly in the product description.
result.actual: The text is misaligned and looks uneven.

result.title: Date picker widget does not show calendar
result.steps:
1. Open the form with the date picker.
2. Click on the date input field.
3. The calendar widget does not appear.
result.expected: The calendar widget should appear when clicking the date input field.
result.actual: The calendar widget does not display.

result.title: App's notification system fails to update
result.steps:
1. Enable notifications for the app.
2. Receive a notification.
3. The notification status does not update after being read.
result.expected: The notification status should change after it is read.
result.actual: The notification status does not update after being read, showing as unread.

result.title: Button not clickable in modal window
result.steps:
1. Open the modal window.
2. Try to click the 'Submit' button.
3. The button does not respond.

result.title: Mobile menu does not open on tap
result.steps: 1. Open the website on a mobile device. 2. Tap the hamburger menu icon. 3. Mobile menu does not open.
result.expected: Mobile menu should open when tapping the menu icon
result.actual: Mobile menu does not respond to taps

result.title: Icons not displaying on dashboard
result.steps:
1. Open the dashboard.
2. Check the icons in the menu bar.
3. Icons are not visible.

result.title: Scroll bar disappears when resizing window
result.steps: 1. Open the website.\n2. Resize the window.\n3. The scroll bar disappears when the window is resized.
result.expected: The scroll bar should remain visible after resizing the window.
result.actual: The scroll bar disappears when the window is resized.

result.title: Pagination does not work on product list
result.steps: 1. Go to the product list page. 2. Click on the next page button. 3. No products load on the next page.
result.expected: Next page should load the products correctly.
result.actual: Pagination does not load the next page, staying on the current page.

result.title: Font size changes unexpectedly after page load
result.steps:
1. Open the homepage.
2. Wait for the page to fully load.
3. Observe that the font size changes for the main text.

result.title: Search functionality returns incorrect results
result.steps:
1. Use the search bar.
2. Type in a relevant keyword.
3. Results are unrelated to the search term.
result.expected: Search results should match the search keyword.
result.actual: Results return irrelevant items that do not match the search term.

result.title: Login form freezes on submit
result.steps:
1. Open the login page.
2. Enter valid login credentials.
3. Click the submit button.
4. The page freezes after clicking submit.

result.title: Checkout page not updating order summary
result.steps:
1. Add an item to the cart.
2. Go to the checkout page.
3. The order summary does not update with the item added.
result.expected: Order summary should reflect the added item.
result.actual: The order summary does not update after adding items to the cart.

result.title: Product image zoom feature broken
result.steps:
1. Open the product page.
2. Click on the zoom feature for product images.
3. Zoom functionality does not work.
result.expected: The product image should zoom in when clicked.
result.actual: Zoom functionality does not activate on product images.

result.title: Social media icons not linking to correct profiles
result.steps:
1. Go to the website.
2. Click on any social media icon.
3. The icon redirects to an incorrect or non-existent profile.

result.title: App icon does not display correctly on home screen
result.steps: 1. Install the app. 2. Add the app icon to the home screen. 3. The app icon displays as a blank square.
result.expected: App icon should display correctly on the home screen.
result.actual: App icon shows as a blank square on the home screen.

result.title: Audio playback issues in mobile app
result.steps:
1. Open the app.
2. Play an audio file.
3. Audio stutters and cuts off unexpectedly.
result.expected: Audio should play smoothly without interruptions.
result.actual: Audio stutters and sometimes cuts off mid-playback.

result.title: User profile picture not updating
result.steps:
1. Go to the user profile page.
2. Upload a new profile picture.
3. The picture does not update after upload.
result.expected: Profile picture should update after upload.

result.title: Page title not updating after navigation
result.steps: 1. Open the website. 2. Navigate to a different page. 3. The page title does not update after navigation.
result.expected: The page title should update when navigating to a new page.
result.actual: The page title remains the same after navigation.

result.title: Slider control not functioning on homepage
result.steps: 1. Go to the homepage. 2. Try using the slider control to view different sections. 3. Slider does not move.
result.expected: Slider should allow users to view different sections.
result.actual: Slider control is unresponsive and does not move.

result.title: Dropdown menu disappears too quickly
result.steps:
1. Hover over the dropdown menu.
2. The menu appears for a split second, then disappears immediately.
result.expected: The dropdown menu should remain open until the user clicks or moves away.
result.actual: The dropdown menu disappears too quickly, making it difficult to select items.

result.title: Page not responsive on iPad
result.steps: 1. Open the website on an iPad. 2. Page does not scale correctly for mobile view.
result.expected: Page should be responsive and adapt to the iPad screen size.
result.actual: Page content is too large and does not scale properly for iPad screen.

result.title: Cart item quantity not updating
result.steps:
1. Add items to the cart.
2. Change the quantity of an item in the cart.
3. The quantity does not update.
result.expected: Cart should update the item quantity accordingly.
result.actual: Item quantity in the cart does not change.

result.title: User settings page loading extremely slowly
result.steps: 1. Open the user settings page. 2. The page takes an unusually long time to load.
result.expected: User settings page should load within a reasonable amount of time.
result.actual: User settings page takes more than 10 seconds to load.

result.title: Email confirmation not being sent after registration
result.steps:
1. Register a new account.
2. Expect an email confirmation.
3. No email confirmation is sent.
result.expected: An email confirmation should be sent after registration to verify the user's email address.

result.title: Video playback controls missing in embedded player
result.steps:
1. Open a page with an embedded video.
2. Try to interact with video controls.
3. Video controls are missing.
result.expected: Video controls should be visible and functional.
result.actual: Video controls are missing, preventing interaction with the video.

result.title: User cannot change password from account settings
result.steps:
1. Go to account settings.
2. Try changing the password.
3. The password change form does not submit.

result.title: Breadcrumb navigation not visible on product pages
result.steps:
1. Go to a product page.
2. Breadcrumb navigation is not displayed at the top of the page.
result.expected: Breadcrumb navigation should be visible on product pages.
result.actual: Breadcrumb navigation is missing from product pages.
